{"tid":2244152,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"青年涉藏伸縮棍 警稱以「曱甴」稱呼示威者「可能係一個代號」","createTime":"2020-10-15T09:29:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-15T11:25:23.000Z","uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"db723474b01660f2ea4b96b9a74384adc0662235","tid":2244152,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T09:29:43.000Z","msg":"伍在辯方盤問下承認，將被告制服是因相信他曾作出破壞社會安寧行為，惟拘捕被告則是因他藏有一支伸縮棍。伍同意沒有證據顯示被告曾參與任何非法活動，亦同意沒有向被告查問伸縮棍是誰擁有。他指按上級指示，只需向被告宣佈拘捕，警誡及查問則留待其他接手警員負責，但承認沒向同袍表示未就被告作出查問或警誡。<br />\n<br />\n辯方指伍制服被告時曾向被告謂「死曱甴仲唔捉到你」，再問被告「有冇衰過」，被告則回應「你查下咪知囉」。伍遂罵被告謂：「死曱甴咁X寸，依家就畀條嘢你。」伍否認。<br />\n<br />\n伍又指有其他警員以「曱甴」稱呼示威者，但形容説法「可能係一個code word（代號）」，並稱自己「冇講過」。審訊下午繼續。"},{"pid":"9e28feae9b249bccee2d0e8ffccdae62db59420d","tid":2244152,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T09:29:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201015/53GVZRT5TFHSXGN5YNDXOUY37E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201015%2F53GVZRT5TFHSXGN5YNDXOUY37E%2F&d=1vxPP2MBW0T8%2FIxNX4ugzv2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=645400c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201015%2F53GVZRT5TFHSXGN5YNDXOUY37E%2F&h=a2e309af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201015/53GVZRT5TFHSXGN5YNDXOUY37E/</a>"},{"pid":"f5f9138c68211c0efbb485386825a4bbfe67a46e","tid":2244152,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T09:31:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8910de1fde44d08781d1cb821cdeaadd30cf330","tid":2244152,"uid":276839,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T09:32:10.000Z","msg":"大方啲，香港有言論自由，唔好學啲玻璃心。"},{"pid":"901469e209b0962c69e215b1f0ca2b7998416e86","tid":2244152,"uid":165749,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T09:32:16.000Z","msg":"黑狗是code word<img src=\"/asset